properties.name: SMOOTH
properties.description: The point is a smooth point, it has two direction lines which are parallel.

properties.name: CORNER
properties.description: The point is a corner point, it has either one direction line, or two independent direction lines.

properties.name: PLAIN
properties.description: The point is a plain point, it has no direction lines.

properties.name: SYMMETRICAL
properties.description: A special type of smooth point with two direction lines of equal length.
